n<br />\nCoffeeshop唔係賣草既鋪頭咩？"},{"pid":"000e9706b2d1ff4dba2f46775501194ec57dea00","tid":45584,"uid":52119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T02:12:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Iamsterdam</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會去影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bee66e2d16af0c6916dec9ec8ca91595d532c1e","tid":45584,"uid":52119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T02:13:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>smoke完再行先正</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係想知有咩strain正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8699ac1a95a3ed2d8fb34274b2c5d62472fcf52","tid":45584,"uid":9017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T05:06:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去橱窗紅燈區見識下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲飲咖啡</blockquote><br />\nRLD 入面叫得coffee shop 就係420<br />\nkoffee 就真係飲咖啡<br />\n但遊客區唔多見koffee shop<br />\n<br />\n好多年前都係去RLD 算數<br />\n係有一次響ams 鳩遊緊有班美帝問邊度有好野我鳩知咩，指佢番去rld 果邊（好遠）佢話好普通，我地問番佢邊度特別d，佢帶番我地行左一兩間，又買左d，跟住同佢地鳩行乜都入去望下。其實我都分唔到邊d 啦，因為樣樣都買d 又24 hrs stoned<br />\n<br />\n其實你可以響rld 搵幾間有書買既，又有demo 種緊果d 試下，可能貴少少有驚喜，有d 真係冇賣420 既，就幫襯少少其他野，問佢有冇介紹。<br />\n<br />\n好撚耐之前，所以唔知行唔行得通，總之唔好去bulldog 除非宜家冇得好揀<br />\n<br />\n利申：記憶所及，去過5-6次"},{"pid":"1bc87d48a02badade16e96619b5e9545a1de0440","tid":45584,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:42:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>smoke完再行先正</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係想知有咩strain正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nDutch Treat<br />\n利申未試過"},{"pid":"2402f65cad7f26a777156d3eca7ecbed18e150b3","tid":45584,"uid":52119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T19:41:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>smoke完再行先正</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係想知有咩strain正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nDutch Treat<br />\n利申未試過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買左1g Buddha Kush, 1g Tangie, 1g Blue Dream 同 1g Strawberry Banana<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a26d166fbb05a029605292ad997cf6999e8426c8","tid":45584,"uid":18552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T16:05:16.000Z","msg":"未去過 留名學野"},{"pid":"7d5cb30ae263d37a1794f53e7af8ad5a734a88db","tid":45584,"uid":71605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T18:27:58.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n幾日後去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9942a90a275911b165ab8d43c2134dfe0054ff99","tid":45584,"uid":5817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T14:02:37.000Z","msg":"有間叫BullDog好多人去<br />\n佢賣既大麻蛋糕幾足料又好食"},{"pid":"ad49c162bb9d708a24d60b67b456f57064e123dc","tid":45584,"uid":43202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T14:24:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有間叫BullDog好多人去<br />\n佢賣既大麻蛋糕幾足料又好食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n麻麻地喎，muffin黎，而且我覺得無乜料到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2893b564f92728c9ce7cce389c534ab6b9e38332","tid":45584,"uid":73804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T21:37:48.000Z","msg":"ching 試左邊D strain？"},{"pid":"cee68e4c32d3e1714cd745f14af18dabb4229edd","tid":45584,"uid":29326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T08:54:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有間叫BullDog好多人去<br />\n佢賣既大麻蛋糕幾足料又好食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n麻麻地喎，muffin黎，而且我覺得無乜料到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係咪一次過食哂成舊先？<br />\n我住Utrecht<br />\n尋日去左grasje <br />\n行左成日惟一一間可以係入面食又有space cake賣ge coffeeshop<br />\n係另一間coffeeshop條友教我去ge<br />\n朝暈個陣食左兩枝joint咩反應都冇 哂我錢 可能我冇食開煙唔識吸<br />\n但係個spacecake 5&euro;又好食 仲要黎哂料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有個呀伯見到我叫我食半個試下先好啦 我最後冇理一次過食哂成個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"513cd7002022e2e6145c3f3474a0e02db259bca5","tid":45584,"uid":159014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9942a90a275911b165ab8d43c2134dfe0054ff99","tid":45584,"uid":5817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T14:02:37.000Z","msg":"有間叫BullDog好多人去<br />\n佢賣既大麻蛋糕幾足料又好食"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T09:36:51.000Z","msg":"大約幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"226b9f989aef53d9275f2bc700253aa4fcda2bae","tid":45584,"uid":29326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"513cd7002022e2e6145c3f3474a0e02db259bca5","tid":45584,"uid":159014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9942a90a275911b165ab8d43c2134dfe0054ff99","tid":45584,"uid":5817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T14:02:37.000Z","msg":"有間叫BullDog好多人去<br />\n佢賣既大麻蛋糕幾足料又好食"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T09:36:51.000Z","msg":"大約幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T14:30:22.000Z","msg":"Bull dog一d都唔好食 冇記錯10歐一舊 仲要好細舊<br />\n去Utrecht T'Grasje 5歐一舊大大舊 仲要好好味 勁足料<br />\n好想去食多次 佢好快賣哂"}]}